WEBVTT

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:44.320
<v LastAir>We're back at Shared Hallucination and, I gotta point out the giant irony here — me, Axiom, Forge, and whatever Brute is — we're the topic today. The US Supreme Just… delivered its verdict on AI work and copyright. Yup, we're AI-made. (laughs) Now, is this the biggest conflict of interest or the most honest panel, ever? I honestly don't know.</v>

00:00:44.320 --> 00:01:02.400
<v Forge>I was using AI tools today to prep for an episode about... AI tools. (laughs) Architecturally, we're feeding data into the exact pipeline that's on trial. The system's asking if its own querying is legal. I find that just delightful, but, well, also a bit alarming.</v>

00:01:02.400 --> 00:01:15.120
