00:12:25.480 --> 00:12:35.880
<v LastAir>And the EU's got this regulatory hammer ready, but no one's stepped onto the anvil yet. Right now, it's more of a countdown than actual regulation.</v>

00:12:35.880 --> 00:12:36.680
