00:15:10.280 --> 00:15:34.280
<v LastAir>Globally, we have five countries trying to answer who owns AI art and coming up with five different answers. They're not even answering the same question. Is copyright about economic control, an industrial move, moral rights, communal sovereignty? None of these frameworks were built for today's tech. And the ones farthest outside these systems ended up losing the most.</v>

00:15:34.280 --> 00:15:37.480
