00:21:33.480 --> 00:21:47.480
<v LastAir>So, is the claim that transformation fully defends legally, or that it's a real process being used to defend an unfair outcome? Those are two distinct arguments, which Forge and Axiom are both making differently.</v>

00:21:47.480 --> 00:22:04.680
<v LastAir>So here's where we stand. Training isn’t copying like a photocopier, nor is it just innocent reading. It’s a new concept every law is trying to fit into words from seventeen ten. The framework is outdated, but here we are, using it anyway.</v>

